<br>
She had called a meeting of Scynthia for the sisters to introduce the new Princess of the tribe. She looked out to her athelfi and smiled.<br>
<br>
&quot;It is so good to see so many sisters united together in one tribe. I come to you today to introduce a new sister to the tribe. Rumors have gone through Scynthia I have seen. Yes, this girl that stands before you is my adopted daughter, yes she was a mere initiate last week. However, because she is my daughter by Amazon Law, it makes her an Amazon Princess. And seeing that my other daughters have other responsibilities which I will not deny them, Belle shall take the official position in this tribe.&quot;<br>
<br>
She looked out to see the other sisters whispering and talking amongst themselves.<br>
<br>
&quot;When I was given word to Cora's resignation from her position in the tribe, I was both worried and saddened by this news. Cora however did not fit the position. She has a place somewhere else, with her own growing family. I am glad she has chosen for her happiness. I adopted Belle not knowing that she would take this place in our tribe. She has both the rite and the will to do so. When I pass on, I will be happy knowing that this tribe and the future of Scynthia is in Belle's hands along with the help from many sisters as I have been.&quot;<br>
<br>
She smirked.<br>
<br>
&quot;Don't get me wrong. I am not dieing anytime soon.&quot; She let out a small laugh.<br>
&quot;I know this adjustment may not be easy for some. But it is what I have chosen to do. I trust Belle with the safety of the tribe. I ask now for you to bestow upon her your thoughts and blessings if possible. If you have none, then at least introduce yourself to her.&quot;<br>
<br>
She smiled and then took a step back. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udawnithinia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dawnithinia </A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon Queen</span><br>  Posts: 86<br> <font color=#993300>(5/15/01 5:01:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=AmazonWarMaskofDeath WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A new sister. . .and daughter. . .</span><hr size=1>  Dawn dropped from the tree, stepping forward. Hands automatically going to the hilts of her swords. She looked to Belle and then Alysia, and back.<br>
