Hipp chuckled at Hera's obvious remark. &quot;Yes, mam. I will go now,&quot; she said and then urged her horse down the hillside to the village and the ceremony.<br>
As she reached the others, she slowed her steed to a slow walk and slowely rode up to the stand.  She stopped her mare and gazed up at Belle.  Her brown eyes now roamed the princess initiate, with having a closer look.  Then slowely raised her hands to bring her wrist gauntlets together in a clink of amazon salute.<br>
&quot;Yasoo athelfi.  Welcome this day your athelfi stand before you.  For it is not for you that you become Princess of this tribe.  It is for them,&quot; Hipp motions to the athelfi standing around. &quot;Make them proud and make them remember you in good name.  Show them your heart and soul is for the Amazon Nation and this tribe.  For it is for them that you now live.&quot;<br>
Hipp gazed at her quietly for a bit watching the young one on the dais. Then a warm smile finally reaches her face. &quot;And we will sing of your name. Blessings, Princess Belle.&quot;<br>
With that and a click of her tongue...Hippolyte's steed began to back up slowely, walking backwards away from Alysia and Belle..pushing the amazons out of it's way.<br>
